casebody.data:
Thursday, April 7, 1994

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-1206. Internatl. Union, United Automobile, Aerospace & Agricultural Implement Workers of Am. v. McFaul.

Cuyahoga County, No. 62286. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective April 6, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
